-- Nasdaq, Ikon Offering Cash-Settled Futures Linked to Spot Gold
-- B y   S t e v e   S t r o t h
-- 2012-02-08T13:50:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-08/nasdaq-ikon-offering-cash-settled-futures-linked-to-spot-gold.html
Nasdaq OMX Group Inc. (NDAQ)  and Ikon Global
Markets Inc. said they will begin offering a cash-settled
futures contract linked to spot gold prices. The contract will
trade under the symbol “NAU” and seeks to simulate the over-
the-counter price of the precious metal, New York-based Nasdaq
OMX said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Steve Stroth in Chicago at 
 sstroth@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
